These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daffodil, tulip, poppy, aconite, iris, lily
The people use 7 different means of transport: van, bus, ship, subway, scooter, train, taxi
 1. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growslily##2
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is in the middle##1
 3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is between the person driving the ship and the person driving the scooter##2
 5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the ship##2
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 9. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
10. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
11. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Flower   | poppy | dahlia | lily | daffodil    | tulip | aconite   | iris    |
| Transport         | train  | bus   | subway | van | ship   | taxi | scooter |

