.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rowing, skateboarding, soccer, cycling, sailing, biathlon, ice-hockey
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: trance, indie, classical, folk, dubstep, country, jazz
1. the fan country is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the fan country##2
3. the fan indie is on the right of the fan trance##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the fan classical##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in the middle##1
6. the fan dubstep is on the left of the fan trance##1
7. the fan jazz is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the fan folk##1
9. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the fan trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Sport          | sailing | soccer | biathlon | skateboarding | ice-hockey | rowing      | cycling  |
| Music-Genre   | country | folk  | jazz     | classical     | dubstep  | trance | indie |

