.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: azure, amber, aquamarine, light-blue, blue, orange, coral
City: paris, rome, venice, new-york, san-francisco, miami, marseilles
 1. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 3. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who likes coral##1
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 5. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 6. the person who likes light-blue is the person traveling to new-york##1
 7. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person who likes light-blue##2
 9. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
10. the person who likes amber is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Color   | coral | blue | azure | amber   | light-blue | aquamarine | orange |
| City           | san-francisco | miami     | rome     | venice | new-york   | paris   | marseilles    |

