.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There 7 different types of food: pomegranate, nectarine, carrot, peach, kiwi, apple, eggplant
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, singing, fishing, chess, drawing, gardening
 1. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 4. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person eating carrot and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
 7. the person eating pomegranate is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person eating nectarine is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Food      | carrot    | kiwi  | peach  | pomegranate  | eggplant      | apple       | nectarine |
| Hobby   | chess | fishing | drawing | gardening | board-games | singing | magic-tricks  |

