.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
7 different pets are kept: mouse, rat, bird, guinea-pig, frog, dog, lizard
7 different games are played: poker, backgammon, whist, monopoly, canasta, go, chess
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing canasta is the owner of the rat##1
3. the person playing poker is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the mouse##2
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
5. the person playing poker is in the middle##1
6. the person playing go is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
8. the person playing backgammon is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
9. the owner of the frog is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig      | frog | mouse | bird | lizard      | rat      | dog |
| Game     | backgammon | go | chess       | poker | whist | canasta | monopoly |

