4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
6. the person traveling to colone is between the person traveling to paris and the person who's birthday is in january##2
7. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Birthday     | march | january | november | february | july | august     | october |
| City   | hannover   | rome    | colone    | paris      | prague  | edinburgh | liverpool |

