 3. the german is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 5. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
 7. the polish is on the right of the german##1
 8. the turkish is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
11. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Hobby   | fishing  | camping   | puzzles         | collecting     | filmmaking              | traveling    | dancing     |
| Nationality        | german | polish | egyptian | brazilian | nigerian | turkish | dutch |

